第一次 (Apple, 2),
=> partition="Apple".hashCode%2=0, key =(partition, "Apple")
=> 最后存入 map key=(0, "Apple"), value=3
第二次 (Pear, 1),
=> partition="Pear".hashCode%2=0, key =(partition, "Pear")
=> 最后存入 map key=(0, "Pear"), value=1
第三次 (Kiwi, 1),
=> partition="Kiwi".hashCode%2=0, key =(partition, "Kiwi")
=> 最后存入 map key=(0, "Kiwi"), value=1
第四次 (Apple, 1),
=> partition="Apple".hashCode%2=0, key =(partition, "Apple")
=> 最后存入 map key=(0, "Apple"), value=2+1=3
